<p rend="centre"> Namo tassa bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa</p>

<p rend="nikaya">Abhidhammapiṭake</p>

<p rend="book">Pañcapakaraṇa-aṭṭhakathā</p>

<p rend="chapter">Dhātukathā-aṭṭhakathā</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Aṭṭhārasahi <pb ed="P" n="0.0114" /><pb ed="M" n="0.0001" /><pb ed="V" n="0.0001" /> bhedehi, vibhaṅgaṃ mārabhañjano;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Desayitvā mahāvīro, yaṃ tasseva anantaraṃ.</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Adesayi dhātukathaṃ, dhātubhedappakāsano;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Tassatthaṃ dīpayissāmi, taṃ suṇātha samāhitāti.</p>
</body>
